<h2 class="bold font-l">Swing Bros</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Mario swings Luigi into the enemy, dealing high damage and launching them into the air. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HumanHammerThrow" class='trope-example-link'>Human Hammer-Throw</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
